  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nSince there are many options for `solc`, can I make `forge build` run my custom command e.g.\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n/usr/local/bin/solc --yul --bin --optimize --optimize-runs 200 --yul-dialect evm $(CONTRACT) | tail -1 > $(OUTPUT_DIR)/bytecode.bin\r\n```\r\n\r\nI have checked the `foundry.toml` configs, but it seems not supported.\r\n\r\n\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
